SECURITY NOTICE:  PhantomChat has not been externally audited. The
cryptographic stack — including PQXDH, Double Ratchet, Sealed Sender,
Dandelion++, Sender Keys, MLS integration, and the Monero-style stealth
address model — is implemented to spec and has an internal integration
test suite, but **must not** be relied upon in life-critical threat
models until a qualified third-party audit is complete.

Report vulnerabilities privately to security@dc-infosec.de before public
disclosure.
